<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="ca"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="genweb6.organs">
<body>

<metal:content-core fill-slot="content" tal:define="sessions view/sessions">

  <h1 class="documentFirstHeading">
    Previsió calendaris de reunions d'òrgans de govern, representació i consulta <tal:year tal:content="view/year"></tal:year>
  </h1>

  <div class="documentDescription">
    <p>La data i hora definitives de les reunions dels òrgans venen fixades per la convocatòria corresponent.</p>
    <p>Si vols que al teu calendari apareguin totes aquestes reunions et pots subscriure al calendari de Reunions d'òrgans de govern, representació i consulta de la UPC al següent <a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/0?cid=dXBjLmVkdV9qZzhuNjU4ZTNwMzc5cjJjNWd1OGhxOG42NEBncm91cC5jYWxlbmRhci5nb29nbGUuY29t" target="_blank">enllaç</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="accordion mb-4" id="accordionSessions">
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseSessions" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSessions">
          <span class="sessions-show"><i class="bi bi-chevron-down me-2"></i>Mostra sessions anteriors</span>
          <span class="sessions-hide d-none"><i class="bi bi-chevron-up me-2"></i>Amaga sessions anteriors</span>
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="collapseSessions" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionSessions">
        <div class="accordion-body p-0">
          <table class="table table-bordered table-hover mb-0">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th style="vertical-align: middle;">
                <span i18n:translate="">Organ</span>
              </th>
              <th style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;" width="110px">
                <tal:head i18n:translate="">Data sessio</tal:head>
              </th>
              <th style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;" width="110px">
                <tal:head i18n:translate="">Horari</tal:head>
              </th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
            <tbody>
          <tal:objects repeat="item sessions/past">
            <tr tal:attributes="class item/id">
              <td style="vertical-align: middle;">
                <i class="bi bi-list"></i>&nbsp;
                    <a tal:attributes="href item/url;" tal:content="item/title" style="color:#007BC0;"> Item Title </a>
              </td>
              <td style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
                <span tal:content="item/date"> Data </span>
              </td>
              <td style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
                <span tal:content="string:${item/start}-${item/end}"> Horari </span>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr tal:condition="item/breakline" class="breakline">
                  <td colspan="3"></td>
            </tr>
          </tal:objects>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <table class="table table-bordered table-hover">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="vertical-align: middle;">
          <span i18n:translate="">Organ</span>
        </th>
        <th style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;" width="110px">
          <tal:head i18n:translate="">Data sessio</tal:head>
        </th>
        <th style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;" width="110px">
          <tal:head i18n:translate="">Horari</tal:head>
        </th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
    <tal:objects repeat="item sessions/future">
      <tr tal:attributes="class item/id">
        <td style="vertical-align: middle;">
          <i class="bi bi-list"></i>&nbsp;
            <a tal:attributes="href item/url;" tal:content="item/title" style="color:#007BC0;"> Item Title </a>
        </td>
        <td style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
          <span tal:content="item/date"> Data </span>
        </td>
        <td style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">
          <span tal:content="string:${item/start}-${item/end}"> Horari </span>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr tal:condition="item/breakline" class="breakline">
          <td colspan="3"></td>
      </tr>
    </tal:objects>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const collapse = document.getElementById('collapseSessions');
      const showText = document.querySelector('.sessions-show');
      const hideText = document.querySelector('.sessions-hide');

      collapse.addEventListener('show.bs.collapse', function () {
        showText.classList.add('d-none');
        hideText.classList.remove('d-none');
      });

      collapse.addEventListener('hide.bs.collapse', function () {
        showText.classList.remove('d-none');
        hideText.classList.add('d-none');
      });
    });
  </script>

</metal:content-core>

</body>
</html>